    MaterialDataTable

    public abstract class AbstractDataTable<T>
extends gwt.material.design.client.base.MaterialWidget
implements DataDisplay<T>
    An abstract data table implementation that can be attached to the DOM. The core functionality is based on the registered DataView, this will handle scaffolding, event registration, and attachment.
    Author:
    Ben Dol
